Package: ecocrop
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of the EcoCrop model for estimating adaptation of plants to environments
Description: The EcoCrop model estimates environmental suitability for plants using a limiting factor approach. The current implementation is flexible; it allows for the use of any environmental predictor, both static (e.g. soil pH) and dynamic (monthly climate data).
Version: 0.0-4
Date: 2020-04-01
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
Imports: meteor, terra, methods (>= 0.2-2), Rcpp (>= 0.12.4)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Authors@R: c(person("Robert J.", "Hijmans", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "r.hijmans@gmail.com"), person("Rhys", "Manners", role = "ctb"))
License: GPL (>=3)
BugReports: https://github.com/cropmodels/ecocrop/issues
URL: https://github.com/cropmodels/ecocrop/

